  <bioghist id="aspace_644f6a979fbb4efa3cc05f6779fb9413">
    <head>BIOGRAPHICAL NOTE</head>
<p>Foster Coffin (class of 1912) was an Alumni Representative at Cornell University and was Director of Willard Straight Student Union, Cornell University.</p>  </bioghist>
  <scopecontent id="aspace_afa9661c67e51ae11ad75d056b9b0f25">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Correspondence with other members of the Cornell Class of 1912 concerning class activities, reunions, and the Donald C. Kerr Memorial Endowment; a small quantity of personal correspondence and financial records; and a phonograph record and tape recording of a portrait presentation ceremony.</p>  </scopecontent>
